I was able to get the url to remove the cache.  It is even more imperative that these be removed now that I know you can actually view the entire document. Thank you so much for all of your help.  Can you please let me know via email when an expected time this will take?  Thank you.  Renea Scott - rscott527@hotmail.com - 641-425-5228
